  <p class="sd:mb-3 sd:text-sm sd:text-gray-600"> 日历支持多种布局尺寸：<code>normal</code>（默认）、<code>sm</code>（紧凑）、<code>xs</code>（超小）、<code>date-picker</code>（日期选择器模式，等同于 xs + month/year/years 视图 + clickToNavigate）。 </p>
  <div class="sd:flex sd:flex-wrap sd:gap-2 sd:mb-3"><span class="sd-radio-group-button sd-radio-group-size-medium sd-radio-group-direction-horizontal"><label class="sd-radio-button sd-radio-checked"><input type="radio" checked="" class="sd-radio-target" value="normal"><span class="sd-radio-button-content">Normal (默认)</span></label><label class="sd-radio-button"><input type="radio" class="sd-radio-target" value="sm"><span class="sd-radio-button-content">sm (紧凑)</span></label><label class="sd-radio-button"><input type="radio" class="sd-radio-target" value="xs"><span class="sd-radio-button-content">xs (超小)</span></label><label class="sd-radio-button"><input type="radio" class="sd-radio-target" value="datePicker"><span class="sd-radio-button-content">date-picker</span></label></span></div>
